  "general": {
    "name": "spPlanTrace",
    "short": "Spectro Arc and Flat Plan Trace Data File for a given MJD and Observatory",
    "description": "The spPlanTrace file contains the plan trace data for a given MJD and Observatory, including information about nightly calibration exposures. It us used to build the traces for the spectrograph data reduction process using an inital set of arc and flat exposures, and correlating theses traces with arc frames taken for each science field during the night",
